      • readTraining

        public void readTraining()
                  throws IOException,
                         ClassNotFoundException
        Reads the associated output training file (located at outputFileLocation). The contents are deserialized into the current learningMachine instance. savedTraining contains a map of: - (Key) The signature contained in the file in the form of numbers separated by spaces. - (Value) The read label(s) at the end of the signature in the form of a sorted set of characters, each a label associated with the signature.
        Throws:
        IOException
        ClassNotFoundException

      • readTraining

        public void readTraining​(String fileLocation)
                  throws IOException,
                         ClassNotFoundException
        Reads the associated output training file (located at outputFileLocation). The contents are deserialized into the current learningMachine instance. savedTraining contains a map of: - (Key) The signature contained in the file in the form of numbers separated by spaces. - (Value) The read label(s) at the end of the signature in the form of a sorted set of characters, each a label associated with the signature.
        Parameters:
        fileLocation - - The location of the training data to be read
        Throws:
        IOException
        ClassNotFoundException
